#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmymoney; Settings"
msgstr "&kmymoney; Nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings described in this chapter modify the behavior of &kmymoney;, "
"allowing you to customize it to meet the needs of your unique financial "
"affairs, and to modify its look and feel to match your personality. These "
"settings can be changed through the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item "
"or by using the keyboard shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;"
"<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo>. In order for any changes to take effect the "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button must be clicked."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve, opisane v tem poglavju, spreminjajo vedenje &kmymoney;, kar vam "
"omogoča, da ga prilagodite potrebam vaših edinstvenih finančnih zadev ter "
"spremenite njegov videz in občutek tako, da ustreza vaši osebnosti. Te "
"nastavitve lahko spremenite v meniju <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"ali z uporabo bližnjice na tipkovnici <keycombo action=\"simul\" >&Ctrl; "
"&Shift;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo>. Če želite, da spremembe začnejo "
"veljati, morate klikniti gumb <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left of the <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> or settings dialog is a "
"list of icons and labels, each representing a particular area of the "
"program. When you click one of those icons, the right part of the dialog "
"will display controls for configuring that area of the program, often "
"divided into several tabs."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani pogovornega okna <guilabel>Konfiguracija</guilabel> ali "
"nastavitev je seznam ikon in oznak, od katerih vsaka predstavlja določeno "
"področje programa. Ko kliknete eno od teh ikon, se v desnem delu pogovornega "
"okna prikažejo kontrolniki za konfiguracijo tega področja programa, ki so "
"pogosto razdeljeni na več zavihkov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

