#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autosave options"
msgstr "Možnosti samodejnega shranjevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An autosave file is just a copy of your data file. The main point of these "
"is that they are automatically created, according to the configuration "
"settings, so you do not need to remember to take any action. Any autosave "
"files created will be in the same directory as the data file currently open."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka za samodejno shranjevanje je samo kopija vaše podatkovne datoteke. "
"Njihova glavna poanta je, da so samodejno ustvarjeni v skladu s "
"konfiguracijskimi nastavitvami, tako da vam ni treba zapomniti ničesar. Vse "
"ustvarjene datoteke za samodejno shranjevanje bodo v istem imeniku kot "
"trenutno odprta podatkovna datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Autosave periodically</guilabel> box instructs "
"&kmymoney; to automatically save your file at the interval defined by the "
"<guilabel>minutes</guilabel> field. The default value is 10 minutes. You can "
"change this setting from 0 (autosave immediately after entering a "
"transaction) up to 60 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje <guilabel>Občasno samodejno shranjevanje</guilabel>, se "
"&kmymoney; samodejno shranjuje vaše datoteke v intervalih, ki jih določa "
"polje <guilabel>minute</guilabel>. Privzeta vrednost je 10 minut. To "
"nastavitev lahko spremenite od 0 (samodejno shranjevanje takoj po vnosu "
"transakcije) do 60 minut."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Autosave when file is modified upon close</guilabel> "
"box instructs &kmymoney; to autosave your file when the program is closed, "
"but only if any changes have been made. You also have the option upon "
"closing the program to backup your &kmymoney; file."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje <guilabel>Samodejno shrani, ko je datoteka spremenjena ob "
"zaprtju</guilabel>, se &kmymoney; samodejno shranjuje  vaše datoteke, ko je "
"program zaprt, vendar le, če so bile narejene kakršne koli spremembe. Imate "
"tudi možnost, da ob zaprtju programa varnostno kopirate datoteko &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Number of backup to keep</guilabel> can be set from 0 (Off) up "
"to 20. The autosave files will be stored in the same folder as the main "
"file. If your data file is MyFinances.kmy, then when an autosave file is "
"created, it will be called MyFinances.kmy.1~. Any existing autosave files "
"will have their number increased by 1, up to the specified number."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Število varnostnih kopij za shranjevanje</guilabel> lahko "
"nastavite od 0 (izklopljeno) do 20. Datoteke za samodejno shranjevanje bodo "
"shranjene v isti mapi kot glavna datoteka. Če je vaša podatkovna datoteka "
"MyFinances.kmy, se bo, ko bo ustvarjena datoteka za samodejno shranjevanje, "
"imenovala MyFinances.kmy.1~. Število vseh obstoječih datotek za samodejno "
"shranjevanje se bo povečalo za 1, do podanega števila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fiscal Year"
msgstr "Fiskalno leto"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; allows you to specify a fiscal year different from the calendar "
"year. To do so, enter the day and month on which your fiscal year begins. "
"This value is used for budgets and some reports."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; vam omogoča, da določite fiskalno leto, ki se razlikuje od "
"koledarskega leta. To storite tako, da vnesete dan in mesec, ko se začne "
"vaše fiskalno leto. Ta vrednost se uporablja za proračune in nekatera "
"poročila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "External programs"
msgstr "Zunanji programi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting does not directly affect the operation of &kmymoney;, but "
"provides a convenient way to launch any external utility, such as an "
"advanced calculator. The first step is to enter the full path to your chosen "
"program in the <guilabel>Calculator</guilabel> text box."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev ne vpliva neposredno na delovanje &kmymoney;, vendar nudi "
"priročen način za zagon katerega koli zunanjega pripomočka, kot je napredni "
"kalkulator. Prvi korak je vnos celotne poti do izbranega programa v "
"besedilno polje <guilabel>Kalkulator</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is currently no direct menu item to launch the calculator, or whatever "
"external program you have set. There are then two ways to launch the program."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno ni neposrednega elementa menija za zagon kalkulatorja ali katerega "
"koli zunanjega programa, ki ste ga nastavili. Obstajata dva načina za zagon "
"programa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, you can use <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars...</guimenuitem> menu item to place the <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-accessories-"
"calculator.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Calculator icon on the Toolbar. Then, when you click that icon on "
"the Toolbar, &kmymoney; will launch the selected application."
msgstr ""
"Najprej lahko uporabite element menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice...</guimenuitem>, da postavite "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-"
"accessories-calculator. svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Ikono kalkulatorja v orodni vrstici. Potem, ko "
"kliknete to ikono v orodni vrstici, &kmymoney;, bo zagnal izbrano aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Second, you can use <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Shortcuts...</guimenuitem> menu item to set a custom keyboard shortcut. (The "
"entry is under &kmymoney;/Calculator in that list.) You can then use that "
"shortcut to launch the application."
msgstr ""
"Drugič, lahko uporabite element menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</guimenuitem>, da nastavite bližnjico "
"na tipkovnici po meri. (Vnos je pod &kmymoney;/Kalkulator na tem seznamu.) "
"Nato lahko uporabite to bližnjico za zagon aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Views tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pogledi"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-settings.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>KMyMoney configuration, general, views tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, splošno, zavihek pogledi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-settings.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>KMyMoney configuration, general, views tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, splošno, zavihek pogledi</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup page options"
msgstr "Možnosti začetne strani"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &kmymoney; starts up, this option indicates whether to start with the "
"Home View (<guilabel>Start with homepage</guilabel>) or with the view "
"displayed when the program was last closed (<guilabel>Start with last "
"selected view</guilabel>.)"
msgstr ""
"Ko se &kmymoney; zažene, ta možnost kaže, ali naj se začne s pogledom domače "
"strani (<guilabel>Začni z domačo stranjo</guilabel>) ali s pogledom, "
"prikazanim ob zadnjem zaprtju programa (<guilabel>Začni z zadnjim izbranim "
"pogledom</guilabel>. )"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type of the &kmymoney; view"
msgstr "Vrsta pogleda &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you select one of three layouts for the View Selector, where you "
"choose Selecting <guilabel>List</guilabel> or <guilabel>Tree</guilabel> "
"view, the icons and their labels will be located at the left side of the "
"window. The List view displays larger icons above the name of each view, "
"while the Tree view has smaller icons to the left of the names. The "
"<guilabel>Tabbed</guilabel> view locates the icons and labels in tabs across "
"the top of the window."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča, da izberete eno od treh postavitev za izbirnik pogleda, kjer "
"izberete pogled <guilabel>Seznam</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Drevo</guilabel>, "
"ikone in njihove oznake se nahajajo na levi strani okna. Pogled seznama "
"prikazuje večje ikone nad imenom vsakega pogleda, medtem ko ima pogled "
"drevesa manjše ikone levo od imen. Pogled <guilabel>Z zavihki</guilabel> "
"najde ikone in oznake v zavihkih na vrhu okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize account selection of Ledgers View and Investments View"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj izbiro računa glavne knjige in pogleda naložbe"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the accounts displayed in the Ledgers View and "
"Investments View will be synchronized, meaning if you change the account "
"displayed in one of the views, and then switch to the other view, the "
"information for the same account will be displayed. This increases the "
"efficiency of navigating between these 2 views. If it is not selected, "
"selecting either of those views will show the same account previously "
"selected in that view, regardless of the account selected in the other view."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, bodo računi, prikazani v Pogledu knjig in Pogledu "
"naložb, sinhronizirani, kar pomeni, da če spremenite račun, prikazan v enem "
"od pogledov, in nato preklopite na drugi pogled, bodo prikazane informacije "
"za isti račun . To poveča učinkovitost navigacije med tema pogledoma. Če ta "
"možnost ni izbrana, bo izbira enega od teh pogledov prikazala isti račun, ki "
"je bil predhodno izbran v tem pogledu, ne glede na račun, izbran v drugem "
"pogledu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Filter"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-settings.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>KMyMoney configuration, general, filter tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, splošno, zavihek filter</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-settings.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>KMyMoney configuration, general, filter tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, splošno, zavihek filter</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: details-settings.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accounts / Categories"
msgstr "Računi / Kategorije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Do not show unused categories</guilabel> box hides "
"unused categories in the Categories View. A hidden category is still "
"available should a transaction require it. By typing a hidden category in "
"the ledger it will become available for use."
msgstr ""
"Če označite polje <guilabel>Ne prikaži neuporabljenih kategorij</guilabel>, "
"skrijete neuporabljene kategorije v Pogledu kategorij. Skrita kategorija je "
"še vedno na voljo, če jo zahteva transakcija. Če skrito kategorijo vnesete v "
"glavno knjigo, bo ta postala na voljo za uporabo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Equity accounts are used to track individual equities or investments held in "
"an Investment Account. These should not be confused with the top level "
"<emphasis>Equity</emphasis> group of accounts, which includes the account(s) "
"which contain the opening balances for other accounts. By default, equity "
"accounts are hidden in the Accounts View. Checking the <guilabel>Show equity "
"accounts</guilabel> box will display the equity accounts in the Accounts "
"View."
msgstr ""
"Računi lastniškega kapitala se uporabljajo za sledenje posameznim lastniškim "
"vrednostnim papirjem ali naložbam na naložbenem računu. Teh ne smemo "
"zamenjevati s skupino računov <emphasis>Lastniškega kapitala</emphasis> na "
"najvišji ravni, ki vključuje račune, ki vsebujejo začetna stanja za druge "
"račune. Privzeto so kapitalski računi skriti v pogledu računov. Če potrdite "
"polje <guilabel>Pokaži račune lastniškega kapitala</guilabel>, boste v "
"Pogledu računov prikazali račune lastniškega kapitala."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, Categories are hidden in the Accounts View. Checking the "
"<guilabel>Show categories in the accounts list view</guilabel> will display "
"the Categories in the Accounts View."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so kategorije skrite v pogledu računov. Če odkljukate "
"<guilabel>Pokaži kategorije v pogledu seznama računov</guilabel>, bodo "
"prikazane kategorije v pogledu računov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Do not show zero balance equities</guilabel> box will "
"remove any zero balance equity accounts from appearing in the Accounts View."
msgstr ""
"Če označite polje <guilabel>Ne prikaži lastniškega kapitala z ničelnim "
"stanjem</guilabel>, boste odstranili morebitne lastniške račune z ničelnim "
"stanjem iz prikaza v Pogledu računov."

#. Tag: term
#: details-settings.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedules"
msgstr "Časovni plani"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Do not show finished schedules</guilabel> box hide "
"all finished schedules from appearing in the Scheduled transactions View."
msgstr ""
"Če odkljukate polje <guilabel>Ne prikazuj dokončanih časovnih planov</"
"guilabel>, skrijete vse dokončane časovne plane iz prikaza v pogledu "
"načrtovanih transakcij."

#. Tag: term
#: details-settings.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transactions"
msgstr "Transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Transactions prior to the date in the <guilabel>Do not show transaction "
"prior to</guilabel> field will not be displayed in the Ledgers View. This "
"can be useful if your data includes many years of transactions; setting this "
"to one or two years ago hides older transactions."
msgstr ""
"Transakcije pred datumom v polju <guilabel>Ne prikaži transakcije pred</"
"guilabel> ne bodo prikazane v Pogledu glavne knjige. To je lahko koristno, "
"če vaši podatki vključujejo večletne transakcije; če to nastavite na eno ali "
"dve leti nazaj, skrijete starejše transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Setting this option to January 1, 1900 (the default value) is a good way to "
"debug date-related data import problems, in case some dates were erroneously "
"very far in the past."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev te možnosti na 1. januar 1900 (privzeta vrednost) je dober način "
"za odpravljanje težav pri uvozu podatkov, povezanih z datumom, v primeru, da "
"so bili nekateri datumi pomotoma zelo daleč v preteklosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Do not show reconciled transactions</guilabel> box "
"will filter transactions by reconciliation state. Transactions that are "
"marked as <emphasis>Reconciled</emphasis> will not be shown in the Ledgers "
"View."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje <guilabel>Ne prikazuj usklajenih transakcij</guilabel>, "
"boste filtrirali transakcije glede na stanje uskladitve. Transakcije, ki so "
"označene kot <emphasis>Usklajene</emphasis>, ne bodo prikazane v Pogledu "
"glavne knjige."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Support tab"
msgstr "Zavihek podpore"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-settings.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>KMyMoney configuration, general section, support tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, splošni razdelek, zavihek podpore</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-settings.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>KMyMoney configuration, general section, support tab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, splošni razdelek, zavihek podpore</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: details-settings.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logging"
msgstr "Beleženje dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; can create a log file when it imports data. This can be useful "
"for troubleshooting problems, but it is important to be careful, as these "
"log files can contain sensitive data, such as usernames and plain-text "
"passwords, as noted in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; lahko ustvari dnevniško datoteko, ko uvozi podatke. To je lahko "
"koristno pri odpravljanju težav, vendar je pomembno, da ste previdni, saj "
"lahko te dnevniške datoteke vsebujejo občutljive podatke, kot so uporabniška "
"imena in gesla v odprtem besedilu, kot je navedeno v pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For any logging to take place, specify the path to the directory where logs "
"will be created in the <guilabel>Log path</guilabel> field. You can also "
"click <guibutton>...</guibutton> to the right of the field, and use the file "
"chooser dialog to navigate to the chosen directory."
msgstr ""
"Za kakršno koli beleženje dnevnika, podajte pot do imenika, kjer bodo "
"dnevniki ustvarjeni v polju <guilabel>Pot dnevnika</guilabel>. Lahko tudi "
"kliknete <guibutton>...</guibutton> na desni strani polja in uporabite "
"pogovorno okno izbirnika datotek za navigacijo do izbranega imenika."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Log imported statements</guilabel> box, whenever "
"&kmymoney; imports data, it will save a file called <quote> <literal>kmm-"
"statement-</literal>yyyy-mm-dd<literal>T</literal>hh-mm-ss.sss<literal>.txt</"
"literal> </quote> in the specified directory. This file is an &XML; file "
"with all the data just imported."
msgstr ""
"Če odkljukate polje <guilabel>Zapisovanje uvoženih zapisov</guilabel>, kadar "
"koli &kmymoney; uvozi podatke, bo shranil datoteko z imenom <quote> "
"<literal>kmm-statement-</literal>yyyy-mm-dd<literal>T</literal>hh-mm-ss."
"sss<literal>.txt</literal> </quote> v navedenem imeniku. Ta datoteka je "
"datoteka &XML; z vsemi pravkar uvoženimi podatki."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Log OFX transactions</guilabel> box, whenever "
"&kmymoney; uses <link linkend=\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect\">OFX direct "
"connect</link> to retrieve transaction data, it will log all the "
"interactions it has with the remote OFX server. It will append these to a "
"file called <literal>ofxlog.txt</literal> in the specified directory. As "
"mentioned above, this file is likely to contain account and user names and "
"plain-text passwords."
msgstr ""
"Če odkljukate polje <guilabel>Zabeleži transakcije OFX</guilabel>, kadar "
"koli &kmymoney; uporablja <link linkend=\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect"
"\">direktno povezavo OFX</link> za pridobivanje podatkov o transakcijah, "
"beleži vse interakcije, ki jih ima z oddaljenim strežnikom OFX. Te bo dodal "
"datoteki z imenom <literal>ofxlog.txt</literal> v navedenem imeniku. Kot je "
"navedeno zgoraj, bo ta datoteka verjetno vsebovala imena računov in "
"uporabnikov ter gesla v odprtem besedilu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Domov"

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home page display sections"
msgstr "Razdelki prikaza domače strani"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-settings.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>KMyMoney configuration, home view</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, domači pogled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-settings.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>KMyMoney configuration, home view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, domači pogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options allow you to customize the appearance of the <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.mainwindow\">Home View</link> (also called the Home Page or Main "
"Window) by choosing which information to display there and the order in "
"which it appears. Selected sections can be reordered by clicking the "
"respective <guibutton>Up</guibutton> or <guibutton>Down</guibutton> button. "
"A section may not appear, even if the appropriate entry is checked, if it "
"would be empty."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti vam omogočajo, da prilagodite videz <link linkend=\"firsttime."
"mainwindow\">pogleda domače strani</link> (imenovane tudi domača stran ali "
"glavno okno), tako da izberete, katere informacije želite tam prikazati in "
"vrstni red, v katerem se prikažejo. Izbrane odseke lahko prerazporedite s "
"klikom ustreznega gumba <guibutton>Gor</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Dol</"
"guibutton>. Razdelek se morda ne prikaže, tudi če je odkljukan ustrezen "
"vnos, če bi bil prazen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assets and Liabilities"
msgstr "Imetja in obveznosti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display a list of asset accounts on the left and liability "
"accounts on the right. These and the other account lists on the Home Page "
"are sorted in alphabetical order, unless otherwise noted. Normally, only "
"open accounts will be listed, unless <link linkend=\"reference.menus.view"
"\">Show all accounts</link> has been selected."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo seznam računov imetij na levi in ​​računov obveznosti na "
"desni. Ti in drugi seznami računov na domači strani so razvrščeni po "
"abecednem vrstnem redu, razen če ni drugače navedeno. Običajno bodo navedeni "
"samo odprti računi, razen če ste izbrali <link linkend=\"reference.menus.view"
"\">Pokaži vse račune</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For this and the other account lists on the Home View, the display will "
"include the account name, date last reconciled, and current balance. In "
"addition, there may be other columns displayed, as configured in the "
"<guilabel>Account information display</guilabel> Lower on this window."
msgstr ""
"Za ta in druge sezname računov v domačem pogledu bo zaslon vključeval ime "
"računa, datum zadnje uskladitve in trenutno stanje. Poleg tega so morda "
"prikazani drugi stolpci, kot je konfigurirano v <guilabel>Prikazu informacij "
"o računu</guilabel> nižje v tem oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduled payments"
msgstr "Načrtovana plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display upcoming occurrences of <link linkend=\"details.schedules"
"\">Scheduled transactions</link>, distinguishing those which are overdue, "
"due today, or due in the future. It shows the date, schedule name, account, "
"and amount of the payment, and the account balance after the payment. By "
"default, it will show up to six transaction. If six are displayed, there is "
"a link you can select to show more, up to 30 days in advance."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo prihajajoče ponovitve <link linkend=\"details.schedules"
"\">Načrtovanih transakcij</link>, pri čemer bo razlikovalo tiste, ki "
"zapadejo, zapadejo danes ali zapadejo v prihodnosti. Prikazuje datum, ime "
"časovnega plana, račun in znesek plačila ter stanje na računu po plačilu. "
"Privzeto bo prikazanih do šest transakcij. Če je prikazanih šest, obstaja "
"povezava, ki jo lahko izberete za prikaz več, do 30 dni vnaprej."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Favorite accounts"
msgstr "Priljubljeni računi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display the accounts that are identified as Favorite accounts in "
"the <guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit account...</guimenuitem> "
"Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo račune, ki so označeni kot Priljubljeni računi v pogovornem "
"oknu konfiguracije <guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi račun...</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payment accounts"
msgstr "Plačilni računi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display all Payment accounts; these include any account into which "
"income can be deposited, and/or out of which bills can be paid."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo vse plačilne račune; ti vključujejo kateri koli račun, na "
"katerega je mogoče nakazati dohodek in/ali s katerega je mogoče plačati "
"račune."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Favorite Reports"
msgstr "Priljubljena poročila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display a list of all reports that have been identified as a "
"favorite in the <link linkend=\"details.reports.config\">Configuration "
"dialog</link> of the Report. The list is in the order of the date when each "
"report became a favorite."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo seznam vseh poročil, ki so bila označena kot priljubljena v "
"<link linkend=\"details.reports.config\">pogovornem oknu konfiguracije</"
"link> poročila. Seznam je po vrstnem redu glede na datum, ko je posamezno "
"poročilo postalo priljubljeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forecast (schedule)"
msgstr "Napoved (časovni razpored)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display a forecast for asset and liability accounts, similar to "
"the <link linkend=\"details.forecast.summary\">Summary Tab</link> of the "
"Forecast View. Details of the display can be controlled with the <link "
"linkend=\"details.forecast.configure\">Forecast Configuration</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo napoved za račune imetij in obveznosti, podobno kot na <link "
"linkend=\"details.forecast.summary\">zavihku Povzetek</link> v pogledu "
"napovedi. Podrobnosti prikaza je mogoče nadzorovati s pogovornim oknom <link "
"linkend=\"details.forecast.configure\">Konfiguracija napovedi</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Net worth forecast"
msgstr "Napoved neto vrednosti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display a chart of your forecast net worth for the next 90 days."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo grafikon vaše napovedane neto vrednosti za naslednjih 90 dni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget"
msgstr "Proračun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display a current month summary and overruns for any <link linkend="
"\"details.budgets\">defined budget(s)</link>. If no budget is defined, it "
"will display no budget or overruns, with the actual current month spending."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo povzetek trenutnega meseca in prekoračitve za vse <link "
"linkend=\"details.budgets\">določene proračune</link>. Če proračun ni "
"določen, bo prikazal brez proračuna ali prekoračitev, z dejansko porabo v "
"tekočem mesecu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cash Flow"
msgstr "Denarni tok"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will display a Cash Flow Summary analysis for the current month."
msgstr "To bo prikazalo analizo povzetka denarnega toka za tekoči mesec."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "Homepage/Summary page scaling"
msgstr "Prilagajanje merila domače strani/strani s povzetkom"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom factor:"
msgstr "Faktor povečave:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows for the selection of the font size as a percentage to fit "
"the Home View based on the user preference."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost omogoča izbiro velikosti pisave v odstotkih, da se prilega "
"domačemu pogledu na podlagi uporabniških preferenc."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remember zoom factor when leaving the program if manually changed with mouse-"
"wheel"
msgstr ""
"Ko zapustite program, si zapomnite faktor povečave, če ga ročno spremenite s "
"koleščkom miške"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this will save your font size preference if you have changed it on "
"the Home page by using the mouse-wheel."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, boste shranili svojo nastavitev velikosti pisave, če "
"ste jo spremenili na domači strani s kolescem miške."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account information display"
msgstr "Prikaz podatkov o računu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options allow you to customize what information is included in any "
"list of accounts on the Home View."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti vam omogočajo, da prilagodite, katere informacije so vključene v "
"kateri koli seznam računov v domačem pogledu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show account limit information"
msgstr "Pokaži podatke o omejitvi računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the account limit as set in the <link linkend=\"details.accounts."
"edit\">Account Edit</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže omejitev računa, kot je nastavljena v pogovornem oknu <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.edit\">Urejanje računa</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show balance-status of mapped online accounts"
msgstr "Prikaži stanje stanj preslikanih spletnih računov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the balance status of mapped accounts, and accounts which have had "
"transactions imported. The status is symbolized by an icon in the column "
"preceding the account name. Note that the colors described here may be "
"different than displayed for you, depending on the display theme selected. A "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-dialog-"
"ok.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"green checkmark indicates the online balance and local balance are the same. "
"A <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-"
"dialog-cancel.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> red warning sign indicates a mismatch between the local file and "
"online-balance. A <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"icon-mail-receive.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> mailbox with a green arrow indicates that the "
"local file has transactions newer than the most recent online update. This "
"alerts the user to perform an online-update."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje stanje stanja preslikanih računov in računov, ki so imeli uvožene "
"transakcije. Status je označen z ikono v stolpcu pred imenom računa. "
"Upoštevajte, da se tukaj opisane barve lahko razlikujejo od prikazanih, "
"odvisno od izbrane teme zaslona. Zelena kljukica <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-dialog-ok.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> označuje, da "
"je spletno stanje in lokalno ravnovesje enako. <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-dialog-cancel.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> "
"</imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> rdeči opozorilni znak "
"označuje neujemanje med lokalno datoteko in spletno bilanco. Nabiralnik "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-mail-"
"receive.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> z zeleno puščico označuje, da lokalna datoteka vsebuje transakcije, "
"ki so novejše od najnovejše spletne posodobitve. To uporabnika opozori, da "
"izvede spletno posodobitev."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show number of not marked transactions per account [!M]"
msgstr "Prikaže število neoznačenih transakcij po računu [!M]"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a column after the account name, showing the number of not marked "
"transactions in the account."
msgstr ""
"Za imenom računa vstavi stolpec, ki prikazuje število neoznačenih transakcij "
"na računu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show number of cleared transactions per account [C]"
msgstr "Pokaži število očiščenih transakcij na računu [C]"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a column showing the number of cleared transactions for the account."
msgstr "Vstavi stolpec, ki prikazuje število očiščenih transakcij za račun."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show number of not reconciled (not marked + cleared) transactions per "
"account [!R]"
msgstr ""
"Prikaže število neusklajenih (neoznačenih + počiščenih) transakcij na račun "
"[!R]"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a column showing the number of not reconciled transactions for the "
"account, &ie;, the sum of all not marked and cleared transactions."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi stolpec, ki prikazuje število neusklajenih transakcij za račun, &ie; "
"vsoto vseh neoznačenih in očiščenih transakcij."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show date of last reconciliation"
msgstr "Prikaži datum zadnje uskladitve"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts an additional column showing the last reconciliation date for the "
"account."
msgstr "Vstavi dodaten stolpec, ki prikazuje zadnji datum uskladitve za račun."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ledger"
msgstr "Glavna knjiga"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings and options in this section allow for the modification of the "
"transaction ledger displayed in the Ledgers View."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve in možnosti v tem razdelku omogočajo spreminjanje glavne knjige "
"transakcij, ki je prikazana v pogledu glavne knjige."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display tab"
msgstr "Zavihek prikaza"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a grid in the ledger"
msgstr "Pokaže mrežo v glavni knjigi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option displays grid lines in the Ledgers View. This is an "
"additional viewing option that may make it easier to visualize separate "
"transactions and their component parts."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, se prikažejo mrežne črte v pogledu glavne knjige. To "
"je dodatna možnost pogleda, ki lahko olajša vizualizacijo ločenih transakcij "
"in njihovih sestavnih delov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show transaction form"
msgstr "Pokaži obrazec transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option displays the <link linkend=\"details.ledger."
"transactionform\">transaction form</link> at the bottom of the ledger, and "
"that is where you enter or edit a transaction. If the transaction form is "
"not displayed, you edit a transaction within the ledger itself. With this "
"option enabled, fewer transactions are visible in the ledger, compared to "
"when it is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, se prikaže <link linkend=\"details.ledger."
"transactionform\">obrazec transakcije</link> na dnu glavne knjige, kjer "
"vnesete ali uredite transakcijo. Če obrazec transakcije ni prikazan, uredite "
"transakcijo v sami knjigi. Ko je ta možnost omogočena, je v knjigi vidnih "
"manj transakcij v primerjavi s stanjem, ko je onemogočena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display overdue schedules with planned date"
msgstr "Prikaži zapadle časovne plane z načrtovanim datumom"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scheduled transactions with future dates are shown in the Ledgers View for "
"the relevant account. When the date passes, and a scheduled transaction "
"becomes overdue, it is no longer shown in the ledger, unless this option is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Načrtovane transakcije s prihodnjimi datumi so prikazane v Pogledu glavnih "
"knjig za ustrezni račun. Ko datum mine in načrtovana transakcija zapade, ni "
"več prikazana v glavni knjigi, razen če je ta možnost izbrana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ledger entry details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti vpisa v knjigo"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show all ledger entries in full detail"
msgstr "Prikaži vse vnose glavne knjige s podrobnostmi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option makes the ledger show all the information for all "
"displayed transactions, with separate lines in the Detail Column for "
"Category, Tags, and the Memo. If it is not selected, Category, Tags, and "
"Memo will not be displayed. This has the same effect as selecting the <link "
"linkend=\"reference.menus.settings.transactiondetail\">Show Transaction "
"Detail</link> menu option."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, bo glavna knjiga prikazala vse informacije za vse "
"prikazane transakcije z ločenimi vrsticami v stolpcu s podrobnostmi za "
"kategorijo, značke in opombo. Če ni izbrana, kategorija, značke in opomba ne "
"bodo prikazani. To ima enak učinek kot izbira menijske možnosti <link "
"linkend=\"reference.menus.settings.transactiondetail\">Pokaži podrobnosti "
"transakcije</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the ledger lens"
msgstr "Uporabi leče glavne knjige"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option displays all the detail lines for the selected "
"transaction, even if <guilabel>Show all ledger entries in full detail</"
"guilabel> is not selected."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, se prikažejo vse vrstice s podrobnostmi za izbrano "
"transakcijo, tudi če ni izbrano <guilabel>Pokaži vse vnose v glavni knjigi v "
"vseh podrobnostih</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show all split details in ledger"
msgstr "Pokaži vse podrobnosti razcepitve v glavni knjigi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting this option shows more details about split transactions."
msgstr ""
"Izbira te možnosti prikaže več podrobnosti o razcepljenih transakcijah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information headers"
msgstr "Glave informacij"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show group headers between transactions"
msgstr "Pokaži glave skupin med transakcijami"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option will display group headers in the ledger. These refer "
"to time periods or milestones such as Last month, Last week, This month, "
"Last reconciliation, Next week, and Next month."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, bodo v glavni knjigi prikazane glave skupin. Ti se "
"nanašajo na časovna obdobja ali mejnike, kot so Prejšnji mesec, Prejšnji "
"teden, Ta mesec, Zadnja uskladitev, Naslednji teden in Naslednji mesec."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show header for the previous and current fiscal year"
msgstr "Pokaži glavo za prejšnje in tekoče fiskalno leto"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option will display group headers in the ledger for the "
"current and the previous fiscal year."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, bodo prikazane glave skupin v glavni knjigi za "
"tekoče in prejšnje fiskalno leto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconciliation group headers"
msgstr "Glave skupin za usklajevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dropdown controls the display of group headers for reconciliations. If "
"<guilabel>Don't show reconciliation entries</guilabel> is selected, then no "
"group headers will be shown for reconciliations. If <guilabel>Show last "
"reconciliation entry with date and balance in ledger</guilabel> is selected, "
"only the most recent reconciliation will be indicated by a group header. If "
"<guilabel>Show all reconciliation entries with date and balance in ledger</"
"guilabel> is selected, then a group header will be shown for all previous "
"reconciliations."
msgstr ""
"Ta spustni meni nadzoruje prikaz skupinskih glav za uskladitve. Če je "
"izbrana možnost <guilabel>Ne prikaži vnosov za usklajevanje</guilabel>, za "
"usklajevanja ne bodo prikazane glave skupin. Če je izbrana možnost "
"<guilabel>Pokaži zadnji usklajevalni vnos z datumom in stanjem v knjigi</"
"guilabel>, bo v glavi skupine prikazana samo zadnja uskladitev. Če je "
"izbrana možnost <guilabel>Pokaži vse vnose usklajevanja z datumom in stanjem "
"v glavni knjigi</guilabel>, bo prikazana glava skupine za vsa prejšnja "
"usklajevanja."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting tab"
msgstr "Zavihek razvrščanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These three sections allow you to set the default sort order of transactions "
"in the Ledgers View. In all cases, the list on the right shows the fields "
"which have been selected as part of the sort order for that view, and the "
"list on the left shows all the fields available for sorting which have not "
"yet been chosen. To sort on an item, select it (single mouse click) and "
"click the right arrow between the two lists. You can adjust the relative "
"order of the fields by selecting one and adjusting its position in the list "
"using the up and down arrows to the right of the list. You can switch "
"between ascending and descending sort for any item by double-clicking it."
msgstr ""
"Ti trije razdelki vam omogočajo, da nastavite privzeti vrstni red transakcij "
"v Pogledu glavne knjige. V vseh primerih seznam na desni prikazuje polja, ki "
"so bila izbrana kot del vrstnega reda za ta pogled, seznam na levi pa "
"prikazuje vsa polja, ki so na voljo za razvrščanje in še niso bila izbrana. "
"Če želite razvrstiti element, ga izberite (enkratni klik z miško) in "
"kliknite desno puščico med obema seznamoma. Relativni vrstni red polj lahko "
"prilagodite tako, da izberete eno in prilagodite njegov položaj na seznamu s "
"puščicama gor in dol na desni strani seznama. Za kateri koli element lahko "
"preklapljate med naraščajočim in padajočim razvrščanjem tako, da ga "
"dvokliknete."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The fields available for sorting are the same for all three sections: "
"Amount, Category, Entry Order (the date the transaction was created, not the "
"internal transaction id,) Number, Payee, Post date, Reconcile state, "
"Reconciliation date, Security, and Type."
msgstr ""
"Polja, ki so na voljo za razvrščanje, so enaka za vse tri razdelke: znesek, "
"kategorija, nalog za vnos (datum, ko je bila transakcija ustvarjena, ne "
"interni ID transakcije), številka, prejemnik plačila, datum knjiženja, "
"stanje uskladitve, datum uskladitve, vrednostni papir in vrsta."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal view subtab"
msgstr "Podzavihek običajnega pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab controls the default sort order of the regular Ledgers View."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek nadzoruje privzeti vrstni red razvrščanja običajnega pogleda "
"glavne knjige."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconciliation view subtab"
msgstr "Podzavihek pogleda usklajevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab controls the default sort order of the ledger while in the "
"Reconciliation View. This is the display of transactions shown during the "
"process of <link linkend=\"details.reconcile\">Reconciliation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek nadzira privzeti vrstni red razvrščanja glavne knjige v pogledu "
"usklajevanja. To je prikaz transakcij, prikazanih med postopkom <link "
"linkend=\"details.reconcile\">Uskladitve</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search view subtab"
msgstr "Podzavihek pogleda iskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab controls the default sort order of the ledger while in the <link "
"linkend=\"details.search\">Search view</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek nadzira privzeti vrstni red razvrščanja glavne knjige v <link "
"linkend=\"details.search\">pogledu iskanja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data Entry tab"
msgstr "Zavihek vnos podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid "These options affect the process of creating new transactions."
msgstr "Te možnosti vplivajo na postopek ustvarjanja novih transakcij."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto increment check number"
msgstr "Samodejno povečanje številke čeka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabling this will automatically increment the check number whenever "
"entering a new check transaction. It has the same effect whether you use the "
"Ledger Lens or the Transaction Form."
msgstr ""
"Če to omogočite, se bo številka čeka samodejno povečala ob vsakem vnosu nove "
"transakcije čeka. Imajo enak učinek ne glede na to, ali uporabljate leče "
"glavne knjige ali transakcijski obrazec."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep changes when selecting a different transaction/split"
msgstr "Ohrani spremembe, ko izberete drugo transakcijo/razcepitev"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, selecting a different transaction or split will save any edits "
"made to the current transaction. When disabled, selecting a different "
"transaction split will prompt you whether or not to save any changes."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, boste z izbiro druge transakcije ali cepitve shranili vse "
"spremembe trenutne transakcije. Ko je onemogočeno, boste z izbiro druge "
"cepitve transakcije pozvani, ali želite shraniti spremembe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Enter to move between fields"
msgstr "Med polji se premikajte s tipko Enter"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, pressing &Enter; will change the focus to the next field of "
"the transaction. When in the last field, the transaction will be saved. When "
"disabled, navigation between fields would occur by using the &Tab; key or "
"the mouse. Pressing the &Enter; key would save the transaction, no matter "
"which field is currently in focus."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, s pritiskom &Enter; bo preusmeril fokus na naslednje polje "
"transakcije. Ko ste v zadnjem polju, bo transakcija shranjena. Ko je "
"onemogočeno, bi navigacija med polji potekala z uporabo &Tab; tipko ali "
"miško. S pritiskom tipke &Enter; bi shranil transakcijo, ne glede na to, "
"katero polje je trenutno v fokusu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match names from start"
msgstr "Ujemanje imen od začetka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option controls <link linkend=\"details.payees.details.matching\">payee "
"matching</link>. When enabled, payee names will always be matched from the "
"start. When disabled, any substring will be matched. Also, when enabled "
"additional options for matching can be established in the Matching Tab of "
"the Payees View."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost nadzira <link linkend=\"details.payees.details.matching"
"\">ujemanje prejemnikov plačil</link>. Ko je omogočeno, se bodo imena "
"prejemnikov vedno ujemala od začetka. Ko je onemogočeno, se bo ujemal kateri "
"koli podniz. Če je omogočeno, lahko na zavihku Ujemanje v pogledu "
"prejemnikov nastavite dodatne možnosti za ujemanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic reconciliation"
msgstr "Samodejno usklajevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option needs to be documented."
msgstr "To možnost je treba dokumentirati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid "Initial cursor position within the date field"
msgstr "Začetni položaj kazalca znotraj datumskega polja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you advance into a transaction's date field (either by creating or "
"editing a transaction, or using &Tab; or &Enter;), this dropdown determines "
"whether the cursor will start in the Day, Month, or Year portion of the date."
msgstr ""
"Ko napredujete v polje datuma transakcije (z ustvarjanjem ali urejanjem "
"transakcije ali z uporabo &Tab; ali &Enter;), ta spustni meni določa, ali se "
"bo kazalec začel v delu datuma, ki je dan, mesec ali leto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default reconciliation state"
msgstr "Privzeto stanje usklajevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dropdown allows you to select the default reconciliation state for new "
"transactions: Not reconciled, Cleared, or Reconciled."
msgstr ""
"Ta spustni meni vam omogoča, da izberete privzeto stanje usklajevanja za "
"nove transakcije: Neusklajeno, Počiščeno ali Usklajeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autofill"
msgstr "Samodejno izpolnjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to select the desired behavior for autofill. This "
"controls which, if any, previous transactions for the same payee are "
"displayed, and which, if any, of those transactions are used to auto-fill "
"details of the new transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča, da izberete želeno vedenje za samodejno "
"izpolnjevanje. To nadzoruje, katere (če sploh) prejšnje transakcije za "
"istega prejemnika plačila so prikazane in katere (če sploh) od teh "
"transakcij se uporabljajo za samodejno izpolnjevanje podrobnosti nove "
"transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid "No Autofill"
msgstr "Brez samodejnega izpolnjevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will deactivate autofill, and you must manually enter all details for "
"the new transaction."
msgstr ""
"To bo deaktiviralo samodejno izpolnjevanje in morali boste ročno vnesti vse "
"podrobnosti za novo transakcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Same transaction if amount differs less than percentage set below"
msgstr ""
"Ista transakcija, če se znesek razlikuje manj od odstotka, določenega spodaj"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option selected, when you enter a new transaction, &kmymoney; will "
"display a list of previous transactions for the same payee and account. If "
"the amount of a previous transaction is close enough to the amount you have "
"entered, it will be considered a match, and details from that previous "
"transaction will be used to autofill details of the new transaction. "
"<quote>Close enough</quote> means within the percentage specified in the box "
"next to <guilabel>Same transaction if amount differs less than</guilabel>, "
"and can range from 0 to 100%. If the percentage is 0, all previous "
"transactions for the payee and account will be displayed, and you can select "
"one of those transactions to use for autofill by clicking it."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, ko vnesete novo transakcijo, &kmymoney; prikaže "
"seznam prejšnjih transakcij za istega prejemnika plačila in račun. Če je "
"znesek prejšnje transakcije dovolj blizu znesku, ki ste ga vnesli, se bo "
"štelo za ujemanje, podrobnosti te prejšnje transakcije pa bodo uporabljene "
"za samodejno izpolnjevanje podrobnosti nove transakcije. <quote>Dovolj "
"blizu</quote> pomeni znotraj odstotka, določenega v polju zraven "
"<guilabel>Ista transakcija, če se znesek razlikuje manj kot</guilabel>, in "
"se lahko giblje od 0 do 100 %. Če je odstotek 0, bodo prikazane vse prejšnje "
"transakcije za prejemnika plačila in račun, s klikom pa lahko izberete eno "
"od teh transakcij, ki jo želite uporabiti za samodejno izpolnjevanje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid "With previously most often used transaction for the payee"
msgstr "S prej najpogosteje uporabljeno transakcijo za prejemnika plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option selected, when you enter new transaction, &kmymoney; will "
"fill in all the transaction details based on the previously most often used "
"transaction for the selected payee."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, ko vnesete novo transakcijo, bo &kmymoney; izpolnil "
"vse podrobnosti transakcije glede na predhodno najpogosteje uporabljeno "
"transakcijo za izbranega prejemnika plačila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use memos from previous transaction"
msgstr "Uporabite opombe iz prejšnje transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, the memo from the previously entered transaction will be "
"automatically entered as the memo for the new transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana, bo opomba iz predhodno vnesene transakcije samodejno vnesena "
"kot opomba za novo transakcijo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:877
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import tab"
msgstr "Zavihek uvoza"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match transaction within days"
msgstr "Ujemanje transakcije v dneh"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search for matching transactions within the range of the imported "
"transaction +/- the given number of days, which can be set from 0 to 99."
msgstr ""
"Poiščite ujemajoče se transakcije v obsegu uvožene transakcije +/- podano "
"število dni, ki jih je mogoče nastaviti od 0 do 99."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ask for a new payee's default category"
msgstr "Zahtevajte novo privzeto kategorijo prejemnika plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:892
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, whenever a new payee is detected during an "
"import, the user will be asked for the default category for the payee."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost izbrana, bo uporabnik vsakič, ko bo med uvozom zaznan nov "
"prejemnik plačila, pozvan k vnosu privzete kategorije za prejemnika plačila."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduled Transactions"
msgstr "Načrtovane transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options allow you to modify the behavior of <link linkend=\"details."
"schedules\">Scheduled Transactions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti vam omogočajo, da spremenite vedenje <link linkend=\"details."
"schedules\">Časovnega načrtovanja transakcij</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup options"
msgstr "Možnosti zagona"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check schedules upon startup"
msgstr "Preverite časovne plane ob zagonu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables checking the schedule upon startup of &kmymoney;. If a scheduled "
"transaction matches the schedule criteria set then &kmymoney; will produce a "
"notification requiring handling of the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča preverjanje časovnega plana ob zagonu &kmymoney;. Če se načrtovana "
"transakcija ujema z nastavljenimi kriteriji časovnega plana, potem "
"&kmymoney; izda obvestilo, ki zahteva obdelavo transakcije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter transactions this number of days in advance"
msgstr "Vnesite transakcije za toliko dni vnaprej"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify how many days in advance a scheduled transaction should be entered."
msgstr "Določite, za koliko dni vnaprej naj se vnese načrtovana transakcija."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Processing Days"
msgstr "Dnevi obdelave"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use holiday calendar for region"
msgstr "Uporabite koledar praznikov za regijo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the region of the world that best suits your needs."
msgstr "Izberite regijo sveta, ki najbolj ustreza vašim potrebam."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ungrouped Item"
msgstr "Nezdružen element"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of days to preview schedules in ledger"
msgstr "Število dni za predogled časovnih planov v glavni knjigi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify how many days in advance should scheduled transactions show up in "
"the ledger. For future scheduled transactions displayed in the ledger, you "
"can enter or skip them by right-clicking them."
msgstr ""
"Določite, koliko dni vnaprej naj se načrtovane transakcije prikažejo v "
"knjigi. Za prihodnje načrtovane transakcije, prikazane v glavni knjigi, jih "
"lahko vnesete ali preskočite tako, da jih kliknete z desno tipko miške."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Quotes"
msgstr "Spletne kotacije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These settings determine how price quotes are retrieved from different "
"online sources. These include stock, bond, and other equity prices, as well "
"as prices for precious metals and currency conversion."
msgstr ""
"Te nastavitve določajo, kako se kotacije cen pridobijo iz različnih spletnih "
"virov. Ti vključujejo cene delnic, obveznic in drugih lastniških vrednostnih "
"papirjev, kot tudi cene plemenitih kovin in pretvorbo valut."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to change the online quote sources for &kmymoney;. "
"Generally speaking, this is an advanced feature, and should only be "
"attempted by the most technically adept users."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča spreminjanje spletnih virov kotacij za &kmymoney;. "
"Na splošno je to napredna funkcija in bi jo morali preizkusiti le tehnično "
"najbolj spretni uporabniki."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more details, please refer to the <link linkend=\"details.investments."
"onlinequotes\">Online Price Quotes</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti si oglejte razdelek <link linkend=\"details.investments."
"onlinequotes\">Spletne kotacije cen</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The initial list and configuration of online quote sources is set up when "
"&kmymoney; first creates your data file. If an online source makes a change "
"which requires a change to these settings in order for &kmymoney; to "
"continue to use it as a valid source, the user must make the necessary "
"changes, using this dialog, based on instructions posted at one of the "
"suggested<link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">support options</link>. "
"Hopefully, in the not to distant future, the way online source configuration "
"is handled will be changed so that &kmymoney; can automatically fetch any "
"necessary updates to these settings without requiring the user to make any "
"manual edits."
msgstr ""
"Začetni seznam in konfiguracija spletnih virov kotacij je nastavljena, ko "
"&kmymoney; najprej ustvari vašo podatkovno datoteko. Če spletni vir naredi "
"spremembo, ki zahteva spremembo teh nastavitev, da &kmymoney; če ga želi še "
"naprej uporabljati kot veljaven vir, mora uporabnik narediti potrebne "
"spremembe z uporabo tega pogovornega okna na podlagi navodil, objavljenih na "
"eni od predlaganih <link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">možnosti podpore</"
"link>. Upajmo, da se bo v ne tako daljni prihodnosti način obravnavanja "
"spletne konfiguracije vira spremenil tako, da bo &kmymoney; lahko samodejno "
"pridobi vse potrebne posodobitve teh nastavitev, ne da bi uporabnik moral "
"ročno urejati."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Barve"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These section allows you to customize the colors used within &kmymoney;. If "
"<guilabel>Custom colors</guilabel> is not checked, then default colors will "
"be used."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča prilagajanje barv, uporabljenih v &kmymoney;. Če "
"<guilabel>Barve po meri</guilabel> niso označene, bodo uporabljene privzete "
"barve."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To customize colors check the <guilabel>Custom colors</guilabel> checkbox. "
"You can then modify any of the colors by clicking the color button, which "
"will open color select palette. This will provide unlimited options in color "
"selection. You can select a defined basic color, pick a color by clicking "
"anywhere on the displayed color palette, input an &HTML; defined color, or "
"specify values for Hue, Saturation, Value, Red, Green, and Blue."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi barve, označite potrditveno polje <guilabel>Barve po "
"meri</guilabel>. Nato lahko spremenite katero koli barvo s klikom na barvni "
"gumb, ki odpre paleto za izbiro barv. To bo zagotovilo neomejene možnosti "
"pri izbiri barv. Izberete lahko določeno osnovno barvo, izberete barvo s "
"klikom kjer koli na prikazani barvni paleti, vnesete &HTML; definirano barvo "
"ali določite vrednosti za odtenek, nasičenost, vrednost, rdečo, zeleno in "
"modro."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to modify the fonts used within the Cell or Header "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča spreminjanje pisav, uporabljenih v poljih Celica ali "
"Glava."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use system fonts"
msgstr "Uporabi sistemske pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this to use system fonts. Deselecting this option allows you to "
"select the fonts of your choice."
msgstr ""
"To izberite za uporabo sistemskih pisav. Če prekličete izbiro te možnosti, "
"lahko izberete pisave po vaši izbiri."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell font"
msgstr "Pisava celice"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the custom font to use within each cell of the ledgers."
msgstr "Določite pisavo po meri za uporabo v vsaki celici glavne knjige."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid "Header font"
msgstr "Pisava glave"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the custom font to use for the headers of each view within the "
"ledger."
msgstr ""
"Določite pisavo po meri, ki bo uporabljena za glave vsakega pogleda znotraj "
"glavne knjige."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option allows for the selection of icons that will be displayed."
msgstr "Ta možnost omogoča izbiro ikon, ki bodo prikazane."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Individual icon settings"
msgstr "Individualne nastavitve ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dropdown list presents a selection of icon themes available for use. "
"Additional icons may be available for downloading and use depending on the "
"operating system or &Linux; Distribution installed."
msgstr ""
"Spustni seznam predstavlja izbor tem ikon, ki so na voljo za uporabo. "
"Dodatne ikone so lahko na voljo za prenos in uporabo, odvisno od "
"operacijskega sistema ali &Linux;, nameščene distribucije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Vtičniki"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section provides information about the available plugins, and allow you "
"to modify the behavior of some of them. Note that the list of plugins "
"displayed will depend on which plugins &kmymoney; found when it started. It "
"does not matter whether the plugin was compiled as part of the application "
"or added as a separate package."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek nudi informacije o razpoložljivih vtičnikih in vam omogoča, da "
"spremenite delovanje nekaterih od njih. Upoštevajte, da bo seznam prikazanih "
"vtičnikov odvisen od tega, kateri vtičniki &kmymoney; so najdeni ob zagonu. "
"Ni pomembno, ali je bil vtičnik preveden kot del aplikacije ali dodan kot "
"ločen paket."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-settings.docbook:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>KMyMoney configuration, plugins</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, vtičniki</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-settings.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>KMyMoney configuration, plugins</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija KMyMoney, vtičniki</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every plugin can be enabled or disabled, according to the state of the "
"checkbox to the left of the name of the plugin name and icon. In addition, "
"at the right, there is an <guibutton>information</guibutton> &infoicon; "
"button for each plugin, which will show the plugin version and author(s.) "
"For some plugins, further information on configuring and using it may be "
"found by clicking &configicon; <guibutton>configure</guibutton> just to the "
"left of the information button."
msgstr ""
"Vsak vtičnik je mogoče omogočiti ali onemogočiti glede na stanje "
"potrditvenega polja na levi strani imena vtičnika in ikone. Poleg tega je na "
"desni strani gumb <guibutton>informacije</guibutton> &infoikona; za vsak "
"vtičnik, ki prikazuje različico vtičnika in avtorja(-e). Za nekatere "
"vtičnike lahko dodatne informacije o konfiguraciji in uporabi najdete s "
"klikom na &configicon; <guibutton>konfiguriraj</guibutton> levo od "
"informacijskega gumba."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Until recently, there was only one plugin that required configuration, the "
"Check printing plugin. Now, there are several plugins which have "
"configuration pages which are invoked from this page. These are listed in "
"the following sections. Note however, that many of them have already been "
"described earlier in this document."
msgstr ""
"Do nedavnega je obstajal le en vtičnik, ki je zahteval konfiguracijo, "
"vtičnik za tiskanje čekov. Zdaj obstaja več vtičnikov s stranmi "
"konfiguracije, ki so priklicane s te strani. Ti so navedeni v naslednjih "
"razdelkih. Upoštevajte pa, da so bili mnogi od njih že opisani prej v tem "
"dokumentu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check printing plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za tiskanje čekov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a plugin for printing checks, which is included with the source of "
"&kmymoney;, and which should always be enabled. It allows printing of a "
"check based on the data from a selected transaction, with the layout "
"controlled by an &HTML; template. You need to use a template which is "
"matched to your pre-printed checks. A default, built-in template is "
"provided. You may also choose a custom template. To do so, click "
"&configicon; <guibutton>configure</guibutton> to get the <guilabel>Check "
"printing</guilabel> configuration dialog displayed. At the top you can check "
"the box to use a custom template. To the right of that is a button which "
"brings up a file chooser, to select an alternate template file."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja vtičnik za tiskanje čekov, ki je vključen v vir &kmymoney; in mora "
"biti vedno omogočen. Omogoča tiskanje čeka na podlagi podatkov iz izbrane "
"transakcije, s postavitvijo, ki jo nadzira &HTML; predloga. Uporabiti morate "
"predlogo, ki se ujema z vašimi vnaprej natisnjenimi čeki. Na voljo je "
"privzeta vgrajena predloga. Izberete lahko tudi predlogo po meri. Če želite "
"to narediti, kliknite &configicon; <guibutton>konfiguriraj</guibutton>, da "
"se prikaže pogovorno okno konfiguracije <guilabel>Tiskanje čekov</guilabel>. "
"Na vrhu lahko potrdite polje za uporabo predloge po meri. Desno od tega je "
"gumb, ki odpre izbirnik datotek za izbiro nadomestne datoteke predloge."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A template file is an &HTML; file, in which specific strings are used to "
"reference fields from the transaction and from the current account and "
"institution to show where they will be printed on the check. &kmymoney; "
"ships with a default, built-in template. At <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde."
"org/office/kmymoney/-/blob/master/kmymoney/plugins/checkprinting/templates/"
"\"> this address</ulink>, you can find the HTML source file of the default "
"template, as well as some additional templates. You should either be able to "
"use one of them or to modify one to suit your needs. Note that only a "
"<emphasis>subset</emphasis> of the HTML standard is supported — the detailed "
"documentation on that can be found <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/"
"richtext-html-subset.html\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka predloge je datoteka &HTML;, v kateri se določeni nizi uporabljajo "
"za sklicevanje na polja iz transakcije ter iz tekočega računa in "
"institucije, da pokažejo, kje bodo natisnjena na čeku. &kmymoney; je "
"dobavljen s privzeto vgrajeno predlogo. Na <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde."
"org/office/kmymoney/-/blob/master/kmymoney/plugins/checkprinting/templates/"
"\"> tem naslovu</ulink> najdete izvorno datoteko HTML privzete predloge, kot "
"tudi nekaj dodatnih predlog. Morali bi imeti možnost, da uporabite enega od "
"njih ali spremenite enega, da bo ustrezal vašim potrebam. Upoštevajte, da je "
"podprt samo <emphasis>podnabor</emphasis> standarda HTML – podrobno "
"dokumentacijo o tem lahko najdete <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/"
"richtext-html- subset.html\">tukaj</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Importer"
msgstr "Uvoznik CSV"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some aspects of configuring the CSV Importer plugin have already been "
"discussed <link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins.csvimporter\">here</"
"link>. However, there is also a dialog which can be invoked here."
msgstr ""
"O nekaterih vidikih konfiguracije vtičnika za uvoz CSV smo že razpravljali "
"<link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins.csvimporter\">tukaj</link>. Vendar "
"pa obstaja tudi pogovorno okno, ki ga lahko prikličete tukaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-settings.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>configure csv importer plugin</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>konfiguriraj vtičnik za uvoz csv</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-settings.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>configure csv importer plugin</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>konfiguriraj vtičnik za uvoz csv</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autodetecting"
msgstr "Samodejno zaznavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is generally best to let the plugin autodetect the field delimiter, "
"decimal symbol, and date format. However, it is possible to disable this "
"behavior for each of these items by unchecking the appropriate box."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno je najbolje, da vtičnik samodejno zazna ločilo polja, decimalni "
"simbol in obliko datuma. Vendar pa je mogoče onemogočiti to vedenje za "
"vsakega od teh elementov tako, da počistite ustrezno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some cases, a csv file to be imported contains the name of the account "
"somewhere in the first lines of the file. You can request the plugin to "
"automatically look for this by checking the appropriate box, separately for "
"banking and for investment imports."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih primerih datoteka csv, ki jo želite uvoziti, vsebuje ime računa "
"nekje v prvih vrsticah datoteke. Zahtevate lahko, da vtičnik samodejno "
"poišče to tako, da označite ustrezno polje, ločeno za bančništvo in za uvoz "
"naložb."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1200
#, no-c-format
msgid "QIF export profile"
msgstr "Izvozni profil QIF"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although it is currently better just to use the QIF exporter plugin "
"directly, it is still possible to have the CSV Importer export a QIF file. "
"In this case, you can use this dropdown to select the default QIF export "
"profile to use."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je trenutno bolje neposredno uporabiti vtičnik izvoznika QIF, je še "
"vedno mogoče, da uvoznik CSV izvozi datoteko QIF. V tem primeru lahko s tem "
"spustnim menijem izberete privzeti izvozni profil QIF, ki ga želite "
"uporabiti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forecast View"
msgstr "Pogled napovedi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is described in the <link linkend=\"details.forecast.configure"
"\">Configuring the Forecast</link> section of the <link linkend=\"details."
"forecast\">Forecast Chapter.</link>"
msgstr ""
"To je opisano v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.forecast.configure"
"\">Konfiguriranje napovedi</link> v <link linkend=\"details.forecast"
"\">poglavju o napovedih.</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1217
#, no-c-format
msgid "iCalendar"
msgstr "iCalendar"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; is capable of exporting a file in the <quote>iCalendar</quote> "
"format, so you can import your scheduled transactions into &korganizer;, or "
"another calendar program, so you can be reminded of scheduled transactions. "
"Actually exporting the file is done with the <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Schedules to "
"iCalendar</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; je sposoben izvoziti datoteko v formatu <quote>iCalendar</quote>, "
"tako da lahko svoje načrtovane transakcije uvozite v &korganizer; ali drug "
"koledarski program, da vas lahko opomnijo na načrtovane transakcije. "
"Pravzaprav se izvoz datoteke izvede z menijsko postavko <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izvozi</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Časovni plani v iCalendar</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-settings.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>configure icalendar export</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>konfiguriraj izvoz icalendar</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-settings.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>configure icalendar export</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>configure icalendar export</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The exported file will contain one event for each scheduled transaction. "
"There are controls to configure whether to have the calendar show reminders "
"for the events, as well as how many reminders, and how far ahead of the "
"events the reminders are created, although these seem not to currently have "
"any effect on the file created."
msgstr ""
"Izvožena datoteka bo vsebovala en dogodek za vsako načrtovano transakcijo. "
"Obstajajo kontrolniki za konfiguracijo, ali naj koledar prikazuje opomnike "
"za dogodke, pa tudi, koliko opomnikov in kako daleč pred dogodki so "
"ustvarjeni opomniki, čeprav se zdi, da ti trenutno ne vplivajo na ustvarjeno "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The final field on the dialog allows you to specify the default name and "
"path of the exported file. As usual, you can either type the full path, or "
"click the file selector icon at the right and get a file selector dialog. "
"Currently, the file save dialog does default to the folder specified here, "
"but you still need to enter the actual file name at the time of export."
msgstr ""
"Končno polje v pogovornem oknu vam omogoča, da določite privzeto ime in pot "
"do izvožene datoteke. Kot običajno lahko vnesete celotno pot ali kliknete "
"ikono izbirnika datotek na desni in prikažete se pogovorno okno izbirnika "
"datotek. Trenutno je pogovorno okno za shranjevanje datoteke privzeto "
"izbrano v mapo, navedeno tukaj, vendar morate še vedno vnesti dejansko ime "
"datoteke v času izvoza."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid "KBanking"
msgstr "KBanking"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin adds support for HBCI/FinTs, OFX, and PayPal online banking by "
"using <ulink url=\"https://www.aquamaniac.de/rdm/\">AqBanking</ulink>, which "
"is an open source project on its own. HBCI/FinTs used to communicate with "
"banks are only used in Germany."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik dodaja podporo za spletno bančništvo HBCI/FinT, OFX in PayPal z "
"uporabo <ulink url=\"https://www.aquamaniac.de/rdm/\">AqBanking</ulink>, ki "
"je samostojen projekt odprte kode. HBCI/FinT, ki se uporablja za "
"komunikacijo z bankami, se uporabljajo samo v Nemčiji."

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuring this plugin is not done through this dialog, but with the <link "
"linkend=\"reference.menus.settings.help\"> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Configure Aqbanking...</guisubmenu> </link> menu item, and there "
"is further information there."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija tega vtičnika ni izvedena prek tega pogovornega okna, ampak z "
"elementom menija <link linkend=\"reference.menus.settings.help\"> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Aqbanking...</"
"guisubmenu> </link > in tam dodatnih informacij."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1274
#, no-c-format
msgid "QIF Exporter, QIF Importer"
msgstr "Izvoznik QIF, uvoznik QIF"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are described in the section on <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qif."
"profile\">QIF Profiles</link>. As pointed out in that section, QIF Import "
"and QIF Export are implemented as separate plugins, they both utilize the "
"same set of profiles."
msgstr ""
"Ti so opisani v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qif.profile"
"\">Profili QIF</link>. Kot je poudarjeno v tem razdelku, sta QIF Import in "
"QIF Export implementirana kot ločena vtičnika, oba uporabljata isti niz "
"profilov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reports view"
msgstr "Pogled poročil"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This provides a dialog where you can configure some default values to be "
"used when displaying <link linkend=\"details.reports\">Reports</link>. The "
"details are described with the other <link linkend=\"details.reports.config."
"plugin\">Report Configuration</link> settings."
msgstr ""
"To ponuja pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko konfigurirate nekatere privzete "
"vrednosti, ki bodo uporabljene pri prikazovanju <link linkend=\"details."
"reports\">Poročil</link>. Podrobnosti so opisane z drugimi nastavitvami "
"<link linkend=\"details.reports.config.plugin\">Konfiguracija poročila</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-settings.docbook:1292
#, no-c-format
msgid "XML Storage"
msgstr "Shramba XML"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default storage of your data is in &XML; format, described in the "
"chapter on <link linkend=\"details.formats\">File Formats</link>. Because "
"the code which reads and saves your data is implemented as a plugin, the "
"configuration dialog which controls some aspects of this storage is accessed "
"through the Plugin section of the general KMyMoney Configuration, although "
"it is described in the above linked section."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto shranjevanje vaših podatkov je v format &XML;, opisan v poglavju o "
"<link linkend=\"details.formats\">Oblikah datotek</link>. Ker je koda, ki "
"bere in shranjuje vaše podatke, implementirana kot vtičnik, se do "
"pogovornega okna konfigracije, ki nadzoruje nekatere vidike tega pomnilnika, "
"dostopa prek razdelka Plugin splošne konfiguracije KMyMoney, čeprav je "
"opisano v zgornjem povezanem razdelku."

